{"tid":1127450,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[259]  若射爆紅軍大門　蘇亞雷斯：我必慶祝","createTime":"2019-04-27T06:28:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-08T00:24:23.000Z","uid":4661,"like":88,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"2f649d950323f93733d2cf9392d15eec2b342268","tid":1127450,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T06:28:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images.performgroup.com/di/library/GOAL/1/da/luis-suarez-barcelona-2018-19_1ofwxaahd6bpk1625qvn4e645g.jpg?t=817045489&amp;quality=60&amp;w=1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.performgroup.com%2Fdi%2Flibrary%2FGOAL%2F1%2Fda%2Fluis-suarez-barcelona-2018-19_1ofwxaahd6bpk1625qvn4e645g.jpg%3Ft%3D817045489%26quality%3D60%26w%3D1600&h=28d0b714&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 巴塞隆拿前鋒蘇亞雷斯，一直對前球會利物浦心懷感激，但於歐聯4強雙方正面對撼，蘇亞雷斯卻謂「落場無父子」，若自己能射破紅軍大門，必定會慶祝入球。<br />\n<br />\n蘇亞雷斯於11至14年效力利物浦，14年幾乎帶領球隊取得英超冠軍，而他亦於紅軍奠定世界級球星地位，令他成為家傳戶曉的名字。雖然已轉會巴塞隆拿，但每次提到紅軍均盡是美言，哨牙蘇對利物浦帶給他的一切，都銘記在心。<br />\n<br />\n但雙方今次於歐聯4強火拚，蘇亞雷斯就說是另一回事，當中不存在友誼：「大家都知利物浦對我的職業生涯好重要，我有好多朋友在當地。不過你亦知道我的為人，每次落到場我都全力以赴，為我效力的球隊付出百分百努力。比賽時不會存在友誼，所以我若取得入球，我是會盡情慶祝。」(<a href=\"http://goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoal.com&d=wHiIeFeeqtLxwJ75m5qcs%2FQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=2b7c34f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"4bf781f850cf0e540760d26cb5a7acd4e2383e26","tid":1127450,"uid":23655,"like":141,"dislike":3,"score":138,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T06:36:46.000Z","msg":"佢最想射爆謝拉特啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73b02a74bb416553a6a6d11752db27ea6fddf609","tid":1127450,"uid":87155,"like":97,"dislike":11,"score":86,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T06:50:03.000Z","msg":"我敢講 佢絕對有資格剷草 打關斗 <br />\n佢同古天奴 幫利付出太多了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢地值得"},{"pid":"09cf0c024d73840dbe1385b4c5021a37c0f2a850","tid":1127450,"uid":90515,"like":12,"dislike":27,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTim